data.text:
Kiwi Kerr takes Olympic gold in bizarre high jump final

New Zealand high jumper Hamish Kerr just kept knocking the bar over - but he still ended up soaring to a bizarrely splendid Olympic gold medal at the Stade de France.

Bengals' Burrow returns, wouldn't mind getting hit next time

In his first game action since suffering a season-ending wrist injury last season, Cincinnati quarterback Joe Burrow didn't get hit during Saturday's preseason opener, a 17-14 loss to the Tampa Bay Buccaneers, untouched in a first-quarter scoring drive.
